143,6 Windows 11 Settings : Make PC & Laptop 200% Faster 👨🏻‍💻,"6 Important Windows 11 Settings Turn on/off Now & Make you PC Faster  2021 : is video mein mene windows 11 se related kuch important settings ke bare mein bataya hai aur sath mein refresh button on kaise krna hai windows 11 meinn ye bhi bataya hai aur kuch tips & tricks share kiye hai jisse aap apne laptop & pc ko ekdam fast bana sakte hai 

--- Copy & paste this Code ----

Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\FeatureManagement\Overrides\4\586118283]

""EnabledState""=dword:00000001

""EnabledStateOptions""=dword:00000001

""Variant""=dword:00000000

""VariantPayload""=dword:00000000

""VariantPayloadKind""=dword:00000000

927,How To import/export contacts Number to Gmail ? phone Number को Gmail id मे कैसे save करे,"imports and export contacts to gmail .
phone no. ko gmail id mai kaise import and export kare.
delete number ko kaise wapas laye.

article padhe :  

Keeping contact lists on
hand and readily available
is important, especially in a
setting where you need to
make calls daily, such as
an office. If contacts are
mainly kept in an Android-
based phone or tablet,
consider copying the
contacts to a Gmail
account. Syncing contacts
with Gmail keeps names
and phone numbers safely
stored online in the Gmail
contacts list if the phone is lost or damaged. To
sync your contacts, add your Gmail account to
the device and enable account synchronization.

Step 1
Press the menu button on the Android device
and tap “Settings.”
Step 2
Tap “Accounts and sync.”
Step 3
Tap the “Add account” button.
Step 4
Tap “Google.”
Step 5
Tap the “Next” button.
Step 6
Tap “Sign in” and enter your Gmail login
information. If you don’t already have a Gmail
account, tap the “Create” button instead and fill
in the form provided.
Step 7
Tap the “Sign in” button. The device will
download the Gmail account’s information.
Step 8
Tap the “Sync Contacts” option.
Step 9
Tap the “Finish” button.

creative story and storyboard with pictures is
drawn on a whiteboard (or something that
resembles a whiteboard) by artists who
record themselves in the process of their
artwork. It is used in TV and internet
advertising to communicate messages in a

930,What is Root ? advantage and disadvantage of Root in hindi ? Root kya ise fayde aur nukshan kya hai,"what is root ?
what is the advantage and disadvantage of root ?
How To Root ?
How To Root Any Android Phone ?

ब्लॉग पढ़े एंड्राइड रूट क्या है 
 

Root क्या है ?
Root के फायदे और नुकशान क्या क्या है ?

Root  कैसे करे ?
इस video को देखे !

Rooting is the process of allowing users of
smartphones , tablets and other devices
running the Android mobile operating system
to attain privileged control (known as root
access) over various Android subsystems. As
Android uses the Linux kernel , rooting an
Android device gives similar access to
administrative ( superuser) permissions as on
Linux or any other Unix-like operating system
such as FreeBSD or OS X .
Rooting is often performed with the goal of
overcoming limitations that carriers and
hardware manufacturers put on some devices.

Advantages
Full theming capabilities, meaning that
everything can be changed and themed from
the color of the battery indicator, to the look
of the dialer or contact list, to the video that
plays while the device boots up.
Full control of the CPU and kernel
Full application control, including the ability
to backup, restore, or batch edit applications,
or to remove bloatware that comes pre-loaded
on many phones.
Processes can be automated on the device
through the use of applications such as
Tasker. 
Ability to install a custom firmware (also
known as a custom ROM) that allows
additional levels of control on a rooted device.
As Android is open source , anyone with the
proper skills can create their own customized
version.

Disadvantage

Bricked Your Phone 
Warranty Finish

932,How To Add Subscribe Button in Youtube videos,"How To Add subscribe button in all youtube videos 

Here are the steps to create a subscribe
button using the Branding Feature:
Click on your Profile Image
Click Creator Studio
Click Channel
Click Branding
Click Add a watermark

youtube video mai subscribe button kese add karte hai !! ?

youtube subscribe button.
add youtube watermark .
add water mark in youtube videos.
To learn How to add a Subscribe Button to your
YouTube Video!, you'll just need to follow these
simple steps:

Step1. Log into your YouTube account and click
""Video Manger"" in the upper middle section, right
below the search box.

step2. Under each video there is a box that says
""edit"" with an arrow pointing down. Click the
arrow of the video you wish to add the subscribe
button to. Once you're decided which video, click
""Annotations"".

Step3. Your video will auto-play, so pause to avoid
distraction. Click ""add annotations"" on the right
side of the page and select ""note"".

Step 4. Decide what placement you want to box to be
located in the video (upper right hand corner is
best) and type out what you want the box to say,
something like ""subscribe to my channel"" or ""like
what you see? Don't forget to subscribe"".
Something catchy and quick.

Step5. After you've done that select what time in the
video that you wish this box to appear.
Step 6. Click the unchecked box that says ""link"" and
enter your URL of your channel. View below for
custom URL's and non-custom URL's.

Step 7. Save and apply changes and you're done,
congrats!

Step 8. Be sure to preview the link and double check
the box once you've finalized it and made it live.
You need to make sure it connects to your page
and no one else's so that you're getting the
subscribers.

Technology gyan se connect rehne k liye subscribe kare !!
